jokes.1: What falls, but never needs a bandage? The rain.

jokes.2: I was going to tell you a joke about boxing but I forgot the punch line.

jokes.3: I'm not a fan of spring cleaning. Let's be honest, I'm not into summer, fall, or winter cleaning either.

jokes.4: Why did the egg hide? It was a little chicken.

jokes.5: What did the dirt say to the rain? If you keep this up, my name will be mud!

jokes.6: Why couldn't the sunflower ride its bike? It lost its petals.

jokes.7: What's an egg's favorite vacation spot? New Yolk City.

jokes.8: I ate a sock yesterday. It was very time-consuming.

jokes.9: What kind of candy do astronauts like? Mars bars.

jokes.10: I wanted to buy some camo pants but couldn't find any.

jokes.11: I ordered a chicken and an egg from Amazon. I'll let you know.

jokes.12: What month is the shortest of the year? May, it only has three letters.

jokes.13: What did the snail who was riding on the turtle's back say? Wheeeee!

jokes.14: I was going to tell a time traveling joke, but you guys didn't like it.

jokes.15: What do you call a lazy kangaroo? A pouch potato.

jokes.16: I used to run a dating service for chickens, but I was struggling to make hens meet.

jokes.17: Why do we tell actors to 'break a leg?' Because every play has a cast.

jokes.18: What does a pig put on dry skin? Oinkment.

jokes.19: What do you call it when a snowman throws a tantrum? A meltdown.

jokes.20: My uncle named his dogs Timex and Rolex. They're his watch dogs.

jokes.21: Did you hear about the guy whose left side was cut off? He's all right now.

jokes.22: How do you open a banana? With a mon-key.

jokes.23: Which is faster, hot or cold? Hot, because you can catch cold.

jokes.24: What did one plate say to the other plate? Dinner's on me.

jokes.25: Why do oranges wear sunscreen? So they don't peel.

jokes.26: My wife told me to stop acting like a flamingo, so I had to put my foot down.

jokes.27: What do you call a pig that does karate? A pork chop.

jokes.28: Where does Batman go to the bathroom? The batroom.

jokes.29: What do you call a pony with a sore throat? A little horse.

jokes.30: What did the left eye say to the right eye? Between you and me, something smells.

jokes.31: What did the mama tomato say to the baby tomato? Catch up!

jokes.32: Why didn't the melons get married? Because they cantaloupe.

jokes.33: What do you call a fake noodle? An impasta.

jokes.34: How did the pig get to the hogspital? In a hambulance.

jokes.35: I'm so good at sleeping I can do it with my eyes closed!

jokes.36: Why does Humpty Dumpty love autumn? Because he had a great fall.

jokes.37: What happens when a strawberry gets run over crossing the street? Traffic jam.

jokes.38: Why did the cow jump over the moon? The farmer had cold hands.

jokes.39: A termite walks into a bar and says, 'So, is the bar tender here?'

jokes.40: How does an octopus go into battle? Well-armed.

jokes.41: What do you call a pudgy psychic? A four-chin teller.

jokes.42: What did one wall say to the other? I'll meet you at the corner.

jokes.43: Why don't sharks eat clowns? Because they taste funny.

jokes.44: A horse walks into a bar. The bartender says, 'Why the long face?'

jokes.45: What did the pirate say when he turned 80? Aye matey.

jokes.46: What's black and white and goes round and round? A penguin in the washing machine.

jokes.47: How do you organize a space party? You planet.

jokes.48: Why couldn't the bicycle stand up by itself? It was two tired.

jokes.49: Did you hear the rumor about butter? Well, I'm not going to spread it.

jokes.50: Why did the student eat his homework? Because his teacher told him it was a piece of cake.

jokes.51: What did one hat say to the other? You wait here, I'll go on ahead.

jokes.52: What do you call a dinosaur that crashes his car? Tyrannosaurus Wrecks.

jokes.53: I couldn't figure out why the baseball kept getting larger. Then it hit me.

jokes.54: What do you call a boomerang that won’t come back? A stick.

jokes.55: What did the full glass say to the empty glass? You look drunk.

jokes.56: How do you stop a bull from charging? Cancel its credit card.

jokes.57: Why don’t we see elephants hiding in trees? Because they’re really good at it.

jokes.58: What’s the difference between a hippo and a zippo? One’s pretty heavy and the other’s a little lighter.

jokes.59: Did you hear the one about the roof? Never mind, it's over your head.

jokes.60: I used to hate facial hair...but then it grew on me.

jokes.61: A cheese factory exploded in France. Da brie was everywhere.

jokes.62: What's a ninja's favorite type of shoes? Sneakers.

jokes.63: What's the best-smelling insect? A deodor-ant.

jokes.64: What do you call a bear without any teeth? A gummy bear.

jokes.65: Why was the coach yelling at the vending machine? He wanted his quarter back.
